26 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 8, Chapter 6, Subchapter 6, is amended
27 to add an additional section to read as follows:
28 8-6-609. Host fee.
29 (a) As used in this section, "host community" means the county and
30 city in which the proposed, current, or expanded site of the solid waste
31 landfill is located.
32 (b)(1) An agreement or contract for a host fee shall not exceed a
33 contract term of four (4) years ending in December of even-numbered years.
34 (2) The agreement or contract for a host fee may be renewed for an additional
35 term not to exceed four (4) years at the same amount of the host fee or
36 renegotiated for a new amount of the host fee.
